  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "DoomZ XIII Over - Graflario",
      "effect": "3 Level 5 monsters\nOnce per turn, you can also Xyz Summon \"DoomZ XIII Over - Graflario\" by using 1 \"DoomZ\" Xyz Monster you control (transfer its materials). You can detach 1 material from this card; add 1 \"DoomZ\" Spell/Trap from your Deck to your hand, then you can destroy 1 card on the field. If this card is destroyed by card effect: You can Special Summon 1 non-Xyz \"DoomZ\" monster from your Deck or GY. You can only use each effect of \"DoomZ XIII Over - Graflario\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
